 470:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_can.c **** /**
 471:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_can.c ****   * @brief  Enables or disabes the CAN Time TriggerOperation communication mode.
